chnical setup\n- **Accessibility:** ADA compliance, parking, transit access, signage\n\n### Technology Stack\n- Video conferencing: Zoom with recording + moderation backup\n- Participant database: REDCap with real-time status tracking\n- Recordings: Encrypted local storage + cloud backup\n- Transcription: Human-verified transcript QA within 48 hours\n\n### Honorariums & Logistics\n- **Per-Participant:** $75 gift card (venue-specific options)\n- **Moderator Incentive:** $200/session\n- **Total 30 Groups Cost:** ~$22,500 (participant + facilitator)\n\n---\n\n## Risk Register & Mitigation\n\n| # | Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |\n|---|------|------------|--------|-----------|\n| **1** | **Low recruitment conversion (<70% of targets)** | Medium | High | \u2022 Pre-recruitment engagement with community orgs; increase screening pool by 25%; offer incentive boosts in weeks 3\u20134 if needed; rolling recruitment windows per city |\n| **2** | **Facility cancellations/unavailability** | Low | High | \u2022 Secure 2 backup venues per city now; contingency budget ($3K); virtual pivot plan for 2\u20133 groups if on-site unavailable; 2-week facility confirmations |\n| **3** | **Moderator illness/absence during groups** | Medium | Medium | \u2022 On-call reserve moderator (Dr. James Liu) pre-briefed; backup scripts & protocols; cross-train 1 admin per city; daily moderator health check-ins starting week 3 |\n| **4** | **Recording/data quality failures (AV, transcript issues)** | Low | High | \u2022 Dual recording setup (primary + backup); test all A/V day-before each session; live transcription monitoring; manual transcript validation QA; encrypted storage redundancy |\n| **5** | **Participant no-shows (>15% per session)** | Medium | Medium | \u2022 SMS reminders 48h + 24h before groups; confirmation calls 72h before; overbooking by 20%; honorarium pre-distribution to incentivize attendance; rapid replacement recruitment list per city on standby |\n\n---\n\n## Key Conta